<h1>Xanthan Gum</h1>
<div class="pronounce-bar">
  <p>[zan-thuhn guhm]</p>
  <%= audio_tag "xanthan.wav" , id: "myAudio"%>
  <button onclick="playAudio()" type="button"><i class="fa fa-volume-up"></i></button>
</div>


<div class="body-title">
  Sugar-like Compound
</div>
<div class="body">
Xanthan gum is created by a sugar fermentation process.
The bacteria Xanthomonas campestris eat simple sugars and turn them into complex carbohydrates that become xanthan gum.
After processing, xanthan gum looks like a white powder.
</div>

